# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# vLLM DGX Spark Configuration — Gemma 4 31B Dense
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Dense model: 31B parameters, all active per token. Apache 2.0 license.
# BF16 weight footprint ≈ 62 GB (fits single B200 110 GB comfortably).
# Strengths: #3 open model on Arena AI, AIME 2026 89.2%, LiveCodeBench 80.0%,
#            256K context, native multimodal (text + image + video),
#            built-in function calling, configurable thinking mode.
# Released: 2026-04-02
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Required for Multi-Node                                                 │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
WORKER_HOST="${WORKER_HOST:-}"
WORKER_IB_IP="${WORKER_IB_IP:-}"
WORKER_USER="${WORKER_USER:-$(whoami)}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Model Settings                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
MODEL="${MODEL:-google/gemma-4-31B-it}"

# Single B200 — dense 31B fits in BF16 without quantization
TENSOR_PARALLEL="${TENSOR_PARALLEL:-1}"

# ~62 GB weights leaves ~37 GB for KV cache at 0.90 util
GPU_MEMORY_UTIL="${GPU_MEMORY_UTIL:-0.90}"

# Native 256K context; conservative default for good KV cache headroom
MAX_MODEL_LEN="${MAX_MODEL_LEN:-65536}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Docker Settings                                                         │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_IMAGE="${VLLM_IMAGE:-nvcr.io/nvidia/vllm:26.03-py3}"
HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME="${HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-head}"
WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME="${WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-worker}"
SHM_SIZE="${SHM_SIZE:-16g}"
RAY_VERSION="${RAY_VERSION:-2.54.0}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Network Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_PORT="${VLLM_PORT:-8000}"
RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT="${RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT:-8265}"
RAY_PORT="${RAY_PORT:-6385}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Storage Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_CACHE="${HF_CACHE:-/raid/hf-cache}"
WORKER_HF_CACHE="${WORKER_HF_CACHE:-${HF_CACHE}}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Authentication                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_TOKEN="${HF_TOKEN:-}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ vLLM Options                                                            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
# Dense model — no expert parallelism
ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL="${ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL:-false}"

SWAP_SPACE="${SWAP_SPACE:-16}"
TRUST_REMOTE_CODE="${TRUST_REMOTE_CODE:-false}"
LOAD_FORMAT="${LOAD_FORMAT:-safetensors}"

# No quantization needed — BF16 fits; enable tool calling
EXTRA_ARGS="--enable-auto-tool-choice --tool-call-parser hermes"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ NCCL/InfiniBand Settings (auto-detected, override if needed)            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
NCCL_DEBUG="${NCCL_DEBUG:-WARN}"
